      "workout_summary": "8m @111W | 4\u00d730s @262W / 30s rec | 1m @111W | 15s @498W | 1m @111W | 10s @654W | 4m @111W | 2m @392W | 8m @111W",
      "description": "In this test, the purpose is to record the best 1-min power. The warm-up consists of low intensity followed by some threshold toggles, then two priming efforts, then on maximal 1-min attempt in the free ride mode. Be aggressive with pacing and don't worry too much about fading in the second half.\n\n- 8m 30-55%\n- 30s 95-105%\n- 30s 45-55%\n- 30s 95-105%\n- 30s 45-55%\n- 30s 95-105%\n- 30s 45-55%\n- 30s 95-105%\n- 1m 30-55%\n- 1m 30-55%\n- 15s 180-200%\n- 1m 30-55%\n- 10s 240-260%\n- 4m 30-55%\n- 2m Freeride 140-160% - mean max power\n- 8m 30-55%"
